{
  "stem": "19596.6",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I couldn't grasp it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because you see, I was living from day to day.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "With me, it's from day to day.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that's my mind, was brainwashed, it was from-- oh, maybe, most of it is from month to month.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And that's-- that's it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That's why I didn't accumulate any properties and things like that, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "For whom, for what, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it-- it-- it probably affects my children as well, you know, in those respects.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I'm getting a pension from Germany but, you know.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "What I went through.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And the operation I had now is also part of it, part of my punishment.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "On my back, when you get older, you get arthritis around the cracks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And that's why I had the operation on the spine.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was straining my-- my [? core ?] spine.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They had to operate and remove two bones from it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So it did affect me quite a bit in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "In the beginning when I was here, I was waking up in sweat and dreams and nightmares.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I have got nothing of that anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How I feel about other people?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, a lot of them I cannot understand, because the sufferings of other people seems to me so minim.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So little.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "With what people suffered during the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there's a lot of very no good people around, people which are really no good.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And sometimes I'm thinking, isn't it pity that so many good ones really had to go.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Thousands, hundreds of thousands.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And you know, I think within myself that people, unless they haven't suffered, it doesn't leave a mark on them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Only people-- not only through the Holocaust, but even people who went through the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
